Body:
Description: Need help troubleshooting access to the AIC, likely a certificate issue that needs to be updated.  
Access Analyzer version 11.6
The customer mistakenly opened this ticket with Auditor as the platform. Updated Platform and put back through the Technical Support Queue.
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Ian Ranstrom, Holly Smith

Steps to Reproduce Updated: Attempt to access AIC using the desktop link.
Server does not respond to the request.

What We've Learned Updated: --------
04/24/2025
--------
The customer changed the server to use HTTPS and port 481, the link on the desktop was using default http:81
It was also noticed that upon trying to access the login, it was failing to resolve the netbios name of the domain and the service doesn't appear to be getting responses from the SQL server.
Next Steps Updated: Customer is going to reboot the server during off hours to see if this helps the service start again correctly and get responses from SQL.
Invitation updated. Attendees: Ian Ranstrom, Holly Smith, William Dammeier
